# DRS environment variables — NAMES and purpose only. NEVER commit real values.
#
# Local dev:  copy to `.env` (git-ignored) and fill in.
# Vercel:     set per environment (Development / Preview / Production) in the
#             project's Environment Variables settings. Adding the Neon (Postgres) and
#             Vercel Blob integrations populates most of these automatically.
#
# Runtime validation of these variables (zod) is implemented with the app in
# DRS-0002 — see prompts/canvas/DRS-0002-20260630-canvas-app-scaffold.md.

# --- Neon Postgres (race / team / lap persistence) ---
# Provisioned via the Vercel Marketplace -> Neon native integration, which sets these
# per environment. Used by @neondatabase/serverless. (@vercel/postgres is deprecated.)
# Pooled connection string (runtime queries).
DATABASE_URL=
# Direct, non-pooled connection (schema migrations).
DATABASE_URL_UNPOOLED=

# --- Vercel Blob (raw timing dumps, exports) ---
# Read/write token for the Blob store.
BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=
